Author: GitHub
Title: "You have to be here": a look inside GitHub Universe 2025
Description:
This is GitHub Universe. Experience the energy, the community, and the announcements from our 2025 event. From the launch of Agent HQ to the hands-on fun of hacking your badge, see why developers from around the world come together to celebrate what it is to build on GitHub. See you next year: October 28-29, 2026!

#GitHubUniverse #GitHub #GitHubUniverse2025
